snippet.title: The Walking Dead: Season Two -- Episode 3 -- 'In Harm's Way' Trailer
snippet.description:
Clementine and her group are captured by a brutally violent new leader. Are you ready to make hard-hitting decisions in order to escape? Only the strong will survive in Episode 3 of The Walking Dead: The Game Season Two, available to download now! 

http://www.telltalegames.com/walkingdead/

Rated Mature: Violence, blood and gore, and strong language
